Routes are used to define route of particular webpage
For Ex. 'https://linkyo.io/resgister' denotes route of a Sign Up page.

Async and Await functions are used when there is no actual data from the front end but to access a virtual data using post method using json.

(req, res) or simply request and response can be use in any kind of process where there is input and output.

res.status(numbers) denotes the reponse in a coded number.. For example 200 = saved successfully, 501 = error.

crypto.js is used to encrypt and decrypt a message.